==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Dotty
<hw>Dot"ty</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[From 2d
<er>Dot</er>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Composed of, or characterized by,
dots.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <ety>[Perh. a different word; cf. <er>Totty</er>.]</ety>
<def>Unsteady in gait; hence, feeble; half-witted.</def>
<mark>[Eng.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Doty</ent>⟦br⟧
